"title": "4230: desert",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4230: desert",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<h2>The desert as a harsh place</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:6\">JER 2:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:4-Isa25:5\">ISA 25:4–25:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:10\">ISA 49:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:26\">JER 4:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:6\">JER 22:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:5\">HOS 13:5</a></p>\n<h2>The desert as a place of human activity</h2>\n<h3>Living in the desert</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:21\">GEN 21:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg1:16\">JDG 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:19\">PRO 21:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:24\">JER 25:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:25\">EZK 34:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:80\">LUK 1:80</a></p>\n<h3>Grazing livestock in the desert</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:1\">EXO 3:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen36:24\">GEN 36:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr5:9\">1CH 5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:5\">JOB 24:5</a></p>\n<h3>Hiding in the desert</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:14-1Sam23:15\">1SA 23:14–23:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:25\">1SA 23:25</a></p>\n<h2>Dying in the desert</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:11-Exod14:12\">EXO 14:11–14:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:49\">JHN 6:49</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:3\">EXO 16:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num3:4\">NUM 3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:29\">NUM 14:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num32:13\">NUM 32:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:5\">1CO 10:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:17\">HEB 3:17</a></p>\n<h2>God leading and caring for his people in the desert</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut2:7\">DEU 2:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:19-Neh9:21\">NEH 9:19–9:21</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:52\">PSA 78:52</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:18\">EXO 13:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:1\">EXO 17:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:5-Exod17:6\">EXO 17:5–17:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:19\">DEU 1:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:2\">DEU 8:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:5\">DEU 29:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:10\">DEU 32:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:7\">JOS 24:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps136:16\">PSA 136:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:10\">AMO 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:36\">ACT 7:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:18\">ACT 13:18</a></p>\n<h2>John the Baptist in the desert</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:4\">MRK 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:3\">MAT 3:3</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:2-Mark1:3\">MRK 1:2–1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:4\">LUK 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:3\">ISA 40:3</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ in the desert</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:1\">MAT 4:1</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:12-Mark1:13\">MRK 1:12–1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:1\">LUK 4:1</a></p>\n<h2>Specific deserts</h2>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:14\">GEN 21:14</a> <em>Beersheba</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:22\">EXO 15:22</a> <em>Shur</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:1\">EXO 16:1</a> <em>sin</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:1-Exod19:2\">EXO 19:1–19:2</a> <em>Sinai</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:16\">NUM 12:16</a> <em>Paran</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num13:21\">NUM 13:21</a> <em>Zin</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num33:8\">NUM 33:8</a> <em>Etham</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut2:26\">DEU 2:26</a> <em>Kedemoth</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh18:12\">JOS 18:12</a> <em>Beth Aven</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:24\">1SA 23:24</a> <em>Maon</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:1\">1SA 24:1</a> <em>En Gedi</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:2\">1SA 26:2</a> <em>Ziph</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:15\">1KI 19:15</a> <em>Damascus</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs3:8\">2KI 3:8</a> <em>Edom</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:16\">2CH 20:16</a> <em>Jeruel</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:20\">2CH 20:20</a> <em>Tekoa</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:8\">PSA 29:8</a> <em>Kadesh</em>; PSA 63:0 <em>Judah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:1\">MAT 3:1</a> <em>Judea</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:26\">ACT 8:26</a> <em>the desert road from Jerusalem to Gaza</em></p>\n<h2>Deserts used figuratively</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:31\">JER 2:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:6\">ISA 35:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:3\">ISA 40:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:12\">JER 50:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:3\">LAM 4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:3\">HOS 2:3</a></p>",
